  "text": "In conclusion, our results confirm, for the Italian population, the recent data published by Eynon et al. [CITATION_1] that ACTN3 R577X polymorphism is not significantly associated with team sport athletic status, when team sport athletes are compared to endurance athletes and nonathletic controls, and the 577RR genotype is overrepresented in power/sprint athletes compared to team sport athletes. ",
